%20all%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20captured%20national%20attention%20and%20was%20widely%20viewed%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foceangate-ceo-stockton-rush-wanted-elon-musk-doomed-titanic-sub-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanifestation%20of%20Rush's%20hubris%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20relentless%20push%20to%20explore%20the%20deep%20sea%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20that%20meant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foceangate-ceo-stockton-rush-broken-some-rules-titanic-sub-remembered-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebending%20a%20few%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFew%20of%20us%20ever%20have%20a%20fatal%20flaw%2C%20and%20Rush%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20Arnie%20Weissmann%2C%20the%20editor-in-chief%20of%20Travel%20Weekly%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BHe%20thought%20he%20was%20right%20or%20he%20wouldn't%20have%20gotten%20in%20%5Bthe%20submersible%5D%20and%20piloted%20it%2C%20but%20that%20was%20a%20fatal%20flaw.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20Guillermo%20S%C3%B6hnlein%2C%20who%20co-founded%20OceanGate%20with%20Rush%20in%202009%2C%20death%20is%20an%20unfortunate%20element%20of%20innovation%20that%20explorers%20can%20only%20hope%20to%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20always%20know%20that%20setbacks%20are%20almost%20just%20part%20of%20the%20exploration%20experience.%20It's%20almost%20in%20the%20definition%20of%20exploration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20gonna%20have%20setbacks%2C%20and%20you%20hope%20that%20the%20setbacks%20don't%20include%20fatalities%2C%20but%20you%20know%20that's%20a%20possibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20death%20does%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bsetback%2C%26quot%3B%20S%C3%B6hnlein%20said%2C%20that's%20when%20you%20should%20push%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20in%20a%20paradoxical%20kind%20of%20way%2C%20that%20drive%20to%20keep%20