%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20house%20is%20surrounded%20by%20their%20lush%20outdoor%20garden.%20A%20dirt%20pathway%20with%20an%20overhead%20trellis%20covered%20in%20creepers%20leads%20from%20the%20gate%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20their%20property%20to%20the%20couple's%20front%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20front%20section%20of%20the%20house%20is%20shielded%20by%20a%20giant%20insect%20net%20%E2%80%94%20meant%20for%20greenhouses%20%E2%80%94%20to%20prevent%20mosquitoes%20from%20entering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20island%20doubles%20as%20a%20dining%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66693df4ed9a404d829cb3ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20island%20doubles%20as%20a%20dining%20table.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20get%20sun%2C%20you%20get%20wind%2C%20you%20get%20rain%20in%20the%20house%20as%20well%2C%20which%20is%20really%20nice%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20get%20bugs%2C%26quot%3B%20Tanguy%2C%2040%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20even%20a%20garden%20inside%20the%20house%2C%20which%20helps%20keep%20their%20home%20cool%20even%20without%20a%20cooling%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20home%20was%20designed%20and%20built%20by%20the%20late%20architect%20Tony%20Gwilliam%2C%20a%20close%20family%20friend.%20The%20inspiration%20behind%20its%20design%20was%20another%20similar%20building%20prototype%20that%20Gwilliam%20had%20constructed%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbloolagoon.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloo%20Lagoon%20Eco%20Village%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20resort%20located%20along%20the%20east%20coast%20of%20Bali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66693e0fe07904901817fc59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20went%20for%20a%20road%20trip%20during%20our%20first%20week%20in%20Bali%2C%20and%20we%20stopped%20by%20the%20Bloo%20Lagoon%20Eco%20Village%20because%20we%20wanted%20to%20see%20their%20permaculture%20garden.%20In%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20garden%20was%20the%20first%20prototype%20of%20our%20house%2C%20and%20we%20just%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20its%20concept%2C%26quot%3B%20Lucie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20six-meter%20cube%20made%20from%20steel%2C%20and%20the%20couple%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20incorporating%20that%20material%20into%20their%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20using%20steel%2C%20you%20can%20have%20very%20small%20foundational%20elements%2C%26quot%3B%20Tanguy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bathroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6666b9a0e079049018174a5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20couple's%20house%20is%20supported%20by%20six%20steel%20pillars%20and%20made%20from%20local%20brick.%20Because%20it's%20light%2C%20the%20house%20can%20also%20be%20taken%20down%20and%20fit%20in%20a%20container%20to%20be%20moved%20if%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20take%20much%20space%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20require%20many%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20Tanguy%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20explained%2C%20Gwilliam%20and%20the%20couple%20were%20inspired%20by%20architect%20R.%20Buckminster%20Fuller's%20ideas%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moma.org%2Fcollection%2Fworks%2F804%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2522How%2520much%2520does%2520your%2520house%2Cweighed%2520only%2520three%2520tons%253B%2520its%5C%