%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Farmie-hammer-cannibalism-accusations-career-death-grateful-1236039526%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTime%20Is%20Ripe%2C%20My%20Re-Entry%20Has%20Begun%26quot%3B%3A%20VK%20Sasikala%20Big%20Announcement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVK%20Sasikala%2C%20confidante%20of%20late%20Chief%20Minister%20J%20Jayalalithaa%20on%20Sunday%20dramatically%20said%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20thought%20that%20the%20AIADMK%20is%20decimated%20in%20view%20of%20its%20recent%20electoral%20drubbing%20as%20her%20'entry%20has%20begun%2C'%20and%20vowed%20to%20usher%20in%20Amma's%20rule%20by%20winning%20the%202026%20Assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20asserted%20that%20she%20would%20question%20the%20government%20as%20the%20'opposition%20party'%20when%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%20did%20not%20ask%20the%20right%20questions%2C%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20leader%20of%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20unsuccessful%20attempts%20over%20a%20considerable%20period%20of%20time%20to%20regain%20control%20of%20the%20AIADMK%20led%20by%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%2C%20Sasikala%2C%20addressing%20her%20supporters%20here%2C%20said%20the%20time%20is%20ripe%20for%20entry%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20time%20I%20have%20been%20telling%20you%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20any%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20apparently%20referring%20to%20her%20stand%20of%20'unifying'%20the%20party%20for%20which%20she%20also%20had%20toured%20several%20regions%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20sure%2C%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20are%20on%20our%20side....%20I%20am%20very%20strong...%20it%20cannot%20be%20thought%20that%20the%20AIADMK%20is%20finished%20and%20it%20is%20because%2C%20my%20entry%20(re-entry)%20has%20commenced%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20amid%20rounds%20of%20applause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20support%20of%20cadres%20and%20people%