20Sikh%2C%20and%20South%20Asian%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718574480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F435vo76_joe-biden_625x300_24_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbest-way-to-end-war-in-gaza-joe-biden-pushes-for-truce-deal-in-eid-message-5905316%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Joe%20Biden%20used%20his%20Eid%20al-Adha%20message%20to%20Muslims%20to%20advocate%20a%20US-backed%20ceasefire%20deal%20in%20Gaza%2C%20saying%20Sunday%20it%20was%20the%20best%20way%20to%20help%20civilians%20suffering%20the%20%26quot%3Bhorrors%20of%20war%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbest-way-to-end-war-in-gaza-joe-biden-pushes-for-truce-deal-in-eid-message-5905316%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbest-way-to-end-war-in-gaza-joe-biden-pushes-for-truce-deal-in-eid-message-5905316%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbest-way-to-end-war-in-gaza-joe-biden-pushes-for-truce-deal-in-eid-message-5905316%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Water%20Shortage%20Feared%20As%20Snow%20Persistence%20In%20Himalayas%20Hits%20Record%20Low%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20Kush%20Himalaya%20is%20experiencing%20significantly%20lower%20snow%20persistence%20this%20year%2C%20raising%20serious%20concern%20over%20water%20security%20for%20downstream%20communities%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20experts%20from%20the%20International%20Centre%20for%20Integrated%20Mountain%20Development%20(ICIMOD)%2C%20a%20Nepal-based%20intergovernmental%20organisation%2C%20have%20urged%20water%20management%20officials%20to%20initiate%20drought%20management%20strategies%20and%20preemptive%20emergency%20water%20supply%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20Kush%20Himalaya%20(HKH)%20region%20heavily%20depends%20on%20the%20cryosphere%20--%20frozen%20water%20on%20the%20Earth's%20surface%2C%20including%20snow%2C%20permafrost%2C%20and%20ice%20from%20glaciers%2C%20lakes%20and%20rivers.%20This%20frozen%20water%20is%20a%20critical%20source%20of%20freshwater%20for%20around%20240%20million%20(24%20crore)%20people%20living%20in%20the%20HKH%20region%20and%20has%20far-reaching%20benefits%20for%20around%201.65%20billion%20(165%20crore)%20people%20downstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnowmelt%20accounts%20for%20around%2023%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20water%20flow%20of%2012%20major%20river%20basins%20originating%20in%20the%20HKH.%20However%2C%20its%20contribution%20varies%20from%20river%20to%20river%2C%20representing%2074%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Amu%20Darya's%20flow%2C%2077%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Helmand's%20flow%2C%20and%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Indus'%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonitoring%20shows%20snow%20levels%20are%20almost%20a%20fifth%20below%20normal%20across%20the%20region%20this%20year%2C%20with%20the%20most%20dramatic%20declines%20in%20the%20west%2C%20where%20its%20contribution%20to%20water%20supply%20is%20the%20highest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnow%20persistence%20dropped%2017%20per%20cent%20below%20normal%20in%20the%20Ganga%20basin%20and%2014.6%20per%20cent%20below%20normal%20in%20the%20Brahmaputra%20basin%2C%20said%20the%20Snow%20Update%20Report%20-%202024%2C%20released%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Helmand%20river%20basin%20shows%20the%20most%20significant%20drop%20in%20snow%20persistence%20at%2031.8%20per%20cent%20below%20normal.%20Its%20previous%20lowest%20level%20was%20in%202018%2C%20with%20a%2042%20per%20cent%20reduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indus%20basin%20has%20fallen%20to%2023.3%20per%20cent%20below%20normal%2C%20the%20lowest%20level%20in%2022%20years.%20The%20previous%20lowest%20year%20for%20this%20basin%20was%202018%2C%20with%20a%209.4%20per%20cent%20shortfall.%20The%20Mekong%20basin%20had%20the%20smallest%20variation%20from%20normal%2C%20with%20snow%20persistence%20around%201%20per%20cent%20below%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20a%20pattern%20of%20decreasing%20amounts%20and%20persistence%20of%20snow%20across%20the%20Hindu%20Kush%20Himalaya%2C%20with%2013%20of%20the%20past%2022%20years%20registering%20lower-than-normal%20seasonal%20snow%20persistence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20ICIMOD%20cryosphere%20specialist%20Sher%20Muhammad%2C%20who%20is%20also%20author%20of%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20researchers%2C%20policymakers%20and%20downstream%20communities.%20Lower%20snow%20accumulation%20and%20fluctuating%20snow%20levels%20pose%20a%20serious%20increased%20risk%20of%20water%20shortages%2C%20particularly%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiriam%20Jackson%2C%20ICIMOD's%20senior%20cryosphere%20specialist%2C%20said%20agencies%20must%20take%20proactive%20steps%20to%20address%20possible%20drought%20situations%2C%20especially%20in%20early%20summer.%20%26quot%3BPlans%20must%20be%20updated%20to%20accommodate%20water%20stress%2C%20and%20communities%20need%20to%20be%20notified%20of%20the%20risks.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBeyond%20that%2C%20it's%20clear%20that%20governments%20and%20people%20in%20this%20region%20need%20urgent%20support%20to%20adapt%20to%20changes%20in%20snow%20patterns%20that%20carbon%20emissions%20have%20already%20locked%20in.%20G20%20countries%20need%20to%20cut%20emissions%20faster%20than%20ever%20before%20to%20prevent%20even%20more%20changes%20that%20could%20prove%20disastrous%20to%20major%20population%20centres%20and%20industries%20reliant%20on%20snowmelt%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experts%20said%20promoting%20rainwater%20harvesting%20and%20establishing%20local%20water%20committees%20may%20help%20mitigate%20the%20immediate%20impacts%20of%20below-normal%20snowfall%20on%20the%20water%20supply%20in%20the%20HKH%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20to%20ensure%20long-term%20resilience%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20countries%20sharing%20trans-boundary%20rivers%20must%20collaborate%20to%20update%20their%20water%20management%20laws.%20Such%20actions%20are%20crucial%20to%20addressing%20water%20shortages%20in%20south%20Asia%2C%20which%20relies%20on%20snowmelt%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718574060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-02%2Fbcoqjnng_himalayas-reuters_625x300_05_February_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwater-shortage-feared-as-snow-persistence-in-hindu-kush-himalaya-hits-record-low-5905286%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Hindu%20Kush%20Himalaya%20is%20experiencing%20significantly%20lower%20snow%20persistence%20this%20year%2C%20raising%20serious%20concern%20over%20water%20security%20for%20downstream%20communities%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwater-shortage-feared-as-snow-persistence-in-hindu-kush-himalaya-hits-record-low-5905286%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwater-shortage-feared-as-snow-persistence-in-hindu-kush-himalaya-hits-record-low-5905286%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwater-shortage-feared-as-snow-persistence-in-hindu-kush-himalaya-hits-record-low-5905286%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Election%20com