0lawsuit%20members%20through%20the%20mail%20and%20digitally%20on%20June%2014.%20The%20settlement%20included%20over%20100%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenale%20Nielsen%20filed%20the%20lawsuit%20against%20Walt%20Disney%20Parks%20and%20Resorts%20in%20November%202021%20after%20she%20purchased%20a%20Dream%20Key%2C%20which%20allows%20guests%20to%20make%20reservations%20at%20Disneyland%20and%20California%20Adventure%20theme%20parks%20without%20additional%20charge%20for%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20said%20Nielsen%20purchased%20the%20Dream%20Key%20for%20%241%2C399%20because%20Disney%20advertised%20it%20as%20having%20%26quot%3Bno%20block-out%20dates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disneyland%20in%20Anaheim%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6619999716bde8d4ead8a562%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDisneyland%20in%20Anaheim%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EMediaNews%20Group%2FOrange%20County%20Register%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShortly%20thereafter%2C%20Ms.%20Nielsen%20attempted%20to%20use%20her%20Magic%20Key%20to%20make%20park%20reservations%20to%20visit%20Disneyland.%20She%20was%2C%20however%2C%20disappointed%20to%20learn%20that%20Disney%20had%20already%20blocked%20out%20many%20days%2C%20including%20all%20weekend%20days%20in%20the%20month%20of%20November%202021%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENielsen%20discovered%20she%20could%20make%20park%20reservations%20and%20purchase%20single-day%20passes%20for%20those%20dates%2C%20but%20they%20were%20unavailable%20to%20Dream%20Key%20holders%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20was%20not%20that%20park%20reservations%20were%20unavailable%2C%20or%20that%20the%20parks%20had%20reached%20their%20capacity%20and%20therefore%20could%20not%20provide%20reservations%20to%20its%20Dream%20Key%20pass%2