0the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20used%20C%C3%A1ceres%2C%20Spain%20as%20the%20primary%20location%2C%20Cond%C3%A9%20Nast%20Traveler%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20who%20saw%20the%20opening%20shots%20of%20episode%20one%20of%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20will%20know%20that%20the%20red-tiled%20rooftops%20and%20winding%20medieval%20roads%20perfectly%20reimagine%20King's%20Landing%20much%20like%20it%20was%20depicted%20in%20the%20original%20show.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhc.unesco.org%2Fen%2Flist%2F384%2F%5C%22%3Eold%20town%20of%20C%C3%A1ceres%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20site%2C%20has%20a%20rich%20history%20of%20its%20own.%20According%20to%20UNESCO%2C%20it%20was%20ruled%20by%20%26quot%3Bpowerful%20rival%20factions%26quot%3B%20between%20the%2014th%20and%2016th%20centuries%20and%20was%20the%20site%20of%20battles%20between%20the%20Moors%20and%20Christians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHere%20we%20see%20King%20Viserys%20and%20young%20Laena%20Velaryon%20walking%20together%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20episode%20two.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221650%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20scene%20from%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon%2C%26quot%3B%20showing%20a%20man%20and%20a%20young%20girl%20walking%20together%20in%20a%20garden%20with%20high%20hedges%20lining%20the%20pathway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F633e1b0fb3e94d001977d05d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221238%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EViserys%20and%20young%20Laena%20in%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20scene%20came%20early%20in%20the%20first%20season%2C%20when%20King%20Viserys%20was%20offered%20the%20young%20Laena%20as%20a%20future%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20botanic%20gardens%20of%20Lloret%20de%20Mar%2C%20Spain%2C%20are%20where%20King%20Viserys%20Targaryen%20