%22%3Etimeshare%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20vacation%20home%20in%20which%20multiple%20people%20share%20ownership.%20They%20purchase%20blocks%20of%20time%20at%20the%20property%20every%20year%20in%20what%20is%20usually%20a%20long-term%20or%20even%20lifetime%20commitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTimeshare%20fraudsters%20aim%20to%20suck%20their%20victims%20dry%2C%20with%20devastating%20consequences%20to%20victims'%20financial%20futures%2C%20relationships%2C%20and%20physical%20and%20emotional%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20Assistant%20Special%20Agent%20in%20Charge%20Paul%20Roberts%2C%20head%20of%20FBI%20New%20York's%20Complex%20Financial%20Crimes%20Branch%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fbi.gov%2Fnews%2Fstories%2Fmexican-cartels-targeting-americans-in-timeshare-fraud-scams-fbi-warns%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20cartels%20further%20cement%20their%20control%20of%20this%20space%2C%20it's%20especially%20critical%20that%20the%20FBI%20take%20the%20lead%20in%20addressing%20this%20threat%20to%20American%20seniors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20says%20the%20Jalisco%20New%20Generation%20Cartel%20is%20the%20primary%20group%20engaging%20in%20timeshare%20fraud%2C%20but%20others%20are%20likely%20using%20independent%20call%20centers%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20fraud%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cartels%20conduct%20%26quot%3Bextensive%20research%20on%20their%20potential%20victims%26quot%3B%20before%20creating%20fake%20documents%20and%20reaching%20out%20to%20them%20through%20phony%20email%20accounts%2C%20according%20to%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout%20the%20process%2C%20the%20fraudsters%20use%20a%20combination%20of%20high-pressure%20sales%20tactics%20and%20cyber-enabled%20fraud%20strategies%2C%20such%20as%20mimicking%20legitimate%20entities'%20email%20addresses%20and%20forging%20official%20documents%2C%20to%20convince%20victims%20that%20each%20phase%20of%20the%20