0statues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20decisions%20made%20without%20any%20proper%20discussion%20and%20deliberation%20with%20relevant%20stakeholders%20are%20against%20the%20rules%20and%20traditions%20of%20our%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20his%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMy%20statement%20on%20relocation%20of%20statues%20of%20major%20leaders%20in%20the%20Parliament%20House%20Complex%20%E2%80%94%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20The%20statues%20of%20many%20great%20leaders%2C%20including%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Dr.%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20their%20prominent%20places%20in%20the%20Parliament%20House%20Complex%20and%20relocated%20to%20a%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1802355743506710723%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20political%20row%20has%20been%20simmering%20for%20weeks%20over%20the%20decision%20to%20shift%20the%20statues%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20BS%20Ambedkar%20and%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji.%20The%20statues%20--%20moved%20first%20during%20the%20building%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20--%20have%20been%20relocated%20to%20a%20new%20spot%20towards%20the%20back%20of%20the%20Parliament%20Complex%2C%20named%20Prerna%20Sthal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20Secretariat%20had%20explained%20the%20decision%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20which%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BDue%20to%20their%20location%20at%20different%20places%20in%20the%20Parliament%20Complex%2C%20visitors%20were%20not%20able%20to%20view%20these%20statues%20conveniently.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20all%20these%20statues%20are%20being%20respectfully%20installed%20in%20a%20grand%20Prerna%20Sthal%20in%20the%20Parliament%20House%20Comple