2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findia-in-talks-with-norways-equinor-for-oil-reserves-says-report-124061600424_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findia-in-talks-with-norways-equinor-for-oil-reserves-says-report-124061600424_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findia-in-talks-with-norways-equinor-for-oil-reserves-says-report-124061600424_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhy%20Teach%20About%20Riots%26quot%3B%3A%20NCERT%20Chief%20Amid%20Row%20Over%20Babri%20Omission%20In%20Books%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHatred%20and%20violence%20are%20not%20subjects%20of%20education%20and%20school%20textbooks%20should%20not%20focus%20on%20them%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20country's%20top%20education%20body%20NCERT%20has%20said%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20the%20latest%20tweaks%20in%20its%20books.%20The%20tweaks%20include%20removal%20of%20references%20to%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20and%20the%20BJP's%20Ram%20Rath%20Yatra%20led%20by%20its%20veteran%20leader%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20curriculum%20prepared%20by%20NCERT%20is%20followed%20by%20nearly%2030%2C000%20schools%20affiliated%20to%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20NCERT%20director%20Dinesh%20Prasad%20Saklani%20rejected%20accusations%20of%20saffronisation%20of%20the%20school%20curriculum%20and%20said%20the%20tweaks%20in%20textbooks%20are%20part%20of%20an%20annual%20revision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20references%20to%20the%20Babri%20masjid%20demolition%20or%20communal%20violence%20in%20its%20wake%20were%20removed%2C%20Mr%20Saklani%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20should%20we%20teach%20about%20riots%20in%20school%20textbooks%3F%20We%20want%20to%20create%20positive%20citizens%2C%20not%20violent%20and%20depressed%20individuals%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShould%20we%20teach%20our%20students%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20they%20become%20offensive%2C%20create%20hatred%20in%20society%20or%20become%20victim%20of%20hatred%3F%20Is%20that%20education's%20purpose%3F%20Should%20we%20teach%20about%20riots%20to%20such%20young%20children...%20when%20they%20grow%20up%2C%20they%20can%20learn%20about%20it%2C%20but%20why%20school%20textbooks.%20Let%20them%20understand%20what%20happened%20and%20why%20it%20happened%20when%20they%20grow%20up.%20The%20hue%20and%20cry%20about%20the%20changes%20is%20irrelevant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20political%20science%20textbook%20for%20Class%2012%20describes%20Ayodhya's%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20which%20was%20demolished%20on%20December%206%2C1992%2C%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bthree-domed%20structure%26quot%3B%20and%20focuses%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20given%20a%20verdict%20in%20favour%20of%20Ram%20temple%2C%20Babri%20masjid%20or%20Ram%20janmabhoomi%2C%20should%20it%20not%20be%20included%20in%20our%20textbooks%2C%20what%20is%20the%20problem%20in%20that%3F%20We%20have%20included%20the%20new%20updates.%20If%20we%20have%20constructed%20new%20Parliament%2C%20should%20our%20students%20not%20know%20about%20it%3F%20It%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20include%20the%20ancient%20developments%20and%20recent%20developments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20allegations%20of%20saffronisation%2C%20Mr%20Saklani%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20something%20has%20become%20irrelevant%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20be%20changed.%20Why%20shouldn't%20it%20be%20changed%3F%20I%20don't%20see%20any%20saffronisation%20here.%20We%20teach%20history%20so%20that%20students%20know%20about%20facts%2C%20not%20for%20making%20it%20a%20battleground%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCERT%20chief%20also%20questioned%20how%20teaching%20about%20the%20Indian%20knowledge%20system%20amounted%20to%20saffronisation.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20are%20telling%20about%20iron%20pillar%20in%20Mehrauli%20and%20saying%20Indians%20were%20way%20ahead%20of%20any%20metallurgical%20scientist%2C%20are%20we%20wrong%3F%20How%20can%20it%20be%20saffronisation%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2061-year-old%20has%20earlier%20headed%20the%20ancient%20history%20department%20at%20Hemvati%20Nandan%20Bahuguna%20Garhwal%20University%20before%20he%20took%20charge%20of%20NCERT%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpdating%20textbooks%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20a%20global%20practice%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20education.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20is%20changed%20is%20decided%20by%20subject%20and%20pedagogy%20experts.%20I%20do%20not%20dictate%20or%20interfere%20in%20the%20process.%20There%20is%20no%20imposition%20from%20the%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20fourth%20round%20of%20revision%20of%20NCERT%20textbooks%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718541420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-12%2Fclassroom-generic_650x400_51482605821.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fncert-babri-demolition-ayodhya-ram-temple-why-teach-about-riots-ncert-chief-amid-row-over-babri-whitewash-in-books-5902382%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hatred%20and%20violence%20are%20not%20subjects%20of%20education%20and%20school%20textbooks%20should%20not%20focus%20on%20them%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20country's%20top%20education%20body%20NCERT%20has%20said%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20the%20latest%20tweaks%20in%20its%20books.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fncert-babri-demolition-ayodhya-ram-temple-why-teach-about-riots-ncert-chief-amid-row-over-babri-whitewash-in-books-5902382%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%