%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esport%E2%80%99s%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20decided%20to%20find%20out%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20the%20Sumo%20Wrestling%20Association%20in%20Churchgate%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20spoke%20to%20them%20about%20my%20dreams%20of%20pursuing%20sumo%20wrestling%20professionally%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20Her%20enthusiasm%20was%20met%20with%20reluctance.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20told%20me%20that%20India%20did%20not%20have%20the%20infrastructure%20for%20the%20sport%20and%20the%20organisation%20was%20not%20supported%20by%20the%20Government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHetal%20would%20have%20to%20find%20her%20own%20sponsor%20if%20she%20was%20keen%20to%20follow%20her%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20her%20Mumbai%20home%20to%20the%20sumo%20rings%20of%20Estonia%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Hetal%20details%20her%20journey%20out%20for%20me%2C%20I%20cannot%20ignore%20the%20fact%20that%20sumo%20wrestling%20is%20a%20sport%20steeped%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dsports%2Bhistory%2Bin%2Bpics%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%26rlz%3D1C1YTUH_enIN1048IN1048%26oq%3Dsports%2Bhistory%2Bin%2Bpics%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bindia%2B%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOTIKCAEQABiABBiiBDIKCAIQABiABBiiBNIBCDg1OTJqMGo0qAIAsAIA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisplays%20of%20strength%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20just%20physical%20but%20emotional.%20While%20Hetal%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20coach%20to%20help%20her%20with%20the%20former%2C%20she%20relied%20on%20herself%20and%20her%20family%20for%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-3-1718375875.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hetal