%98I%20was%20celebrated%20for%20my%20strength%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20teenager%2C%20the%20memory%20of%20standing%20on%20foreign%20ground%20when%20she%20landed%20in%20Estonia%20is%20still%20fresh%20in%20Hetal%E2%80%99s%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20aware%20that%20no%20one%20from%20India%20would%20be%20there%20at%20the%20tournament%20and%20was%20nervous.%20Here%20I%20was%2C%20going%20for%20something%20that%20was%20so%20new%2C%20and%20in%20a%20strange%20place.%20While%20I%20managed%20to%20find%20a%20sponsor%2C%20the%20funds%20were%20limited%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20be%20extremely%20careful%20about%20budgeting.%20But%20while%20the%20fear%20of%20it%20all%20set%20in%2C%20so%20did%20luck%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mayor%20of%20the%20town%20came%20personally%20to%20receive%20me%20at%20the%20airport%20and%20shared%20how%20happy%20he%20was%20that%20someone%20from%20India%20was%20participating.%20The%20organisers%20saw%20to%20it%20that%20my%20vegetarian%20food%20preferences%20were%20taken%20care%20of%20and%20that%20a%20representative%20accompanied%20me%20at%20all%20times%20so%20that%20language%20barrier%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-2-1718375748.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Following%20the%20success%20at%20the%20World%20Championship%20in%202008%2C%20Hetal%20was%20selected%20for%20World%20Games%20in%202009%20where%20she%20excelled%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-2-1718375748.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-2-1718375748-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu