Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20hopeful%20that%20her%20story%20will%20be%20a%20beacon%20for%20people%20to%20believe%20in%20themselves%20and%20follow%20their%20calling.%20And%20behind%20Hetal%20stands%20a%20proud%20father%20who%20never%20for%20once%20doubted%20that%20his%20daughter%20would%20achieve%20these%20feats%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMhari%20chori%20chore%20se%20kam%20hai%20ke%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20all%20those%20who%20questioned%20how%20Hetal%E2%80%99s%20simple%20diet%20would%20let%20her%20achieve%20greatness%20in%20sports%2C%20her%20father%20has%20an%20answer%20ready%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EEk%20marwari%20ne%20daal%20bhat%20kha%20ke%20history%20bana%20li%3C%2Fem%3E%20(A%20%3Cem%3EMarwari%3C%2Fem%3E%20girl%20has%20created%20history%20despite%20a%20simple%20vegetarian%20diet).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718377969000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D353156%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20often%20celebrate%20the%20accolades%20and%20glory%20that%20sumo%20wrestler%20Hetal%20Dave%20brought%20to%20India.%20Today%20we%20take%20a%20moment%20to%20celebrate%20the%20man%20who%20made%20it%20possible%2C%20Hetal's%20'papa'%20who%20became%20a%20coach%20so%20his%20daughter%20could%20live%20her%20dream.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aamor%C3%A9%3A%20How%20300%20Small%20Farmers%20Are%20Taking%20Alphonso%20Mangoes%20to%20The%20World%20Without%20Middlemen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EConsidered%20the%20king%20of%20mangoes%2C%20Alphonso%20is%20highly%20sought%20after%20by%20mango%20lovers%20across%20the%20world%20for%20its%20distinct%20succulent%20flavour%2C%20aroma%2C%20and%20creamy%20and%20tender%20texture.%20For%20its%20cultivators%20in%20Ratnagiri%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20GI-tagged%20fruit%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prized%20possessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20fruit%20brought%20more%20sweet%20tidings%20for%20its%20farmers%20in%20Ratnagiri%20as%20300%20small%20farmers%20took%20a%20bold%20step%20of%20taking%20Alphonsos%20to%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMango%20export%20is%20a%20highly%20untapped%20market%20in%20Maharashtra.%20We%2C%20local%20farmers%2C%20underestimated%20our%20capabilities%20initially%2C%20worrying%20about%20the%20possible%20chaos%20of%20export%20business.%20We%20knew%20the%20real%20worth%20of%20our%20authentic%20produce%20but%20feared%20getting%20into%20any%20kind%20of%20trap%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejas%20Kawathekar%2C%20director%20of%20farmer%20producer%20company%2C%20Konkan%20Ratnagiri%20Boomi%20Agro%20Producer%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20tap%20the%20global%20market%2C%20the%20farmer%20producer%20company%20decided%20to%20get%20into%20the%20forward%20value%20chain%20and%20export%20the%20produce%20directly%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1718354069.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aamore%20exported%20its%20mangoes%20to%20London%2C%20Canada%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20Kuwait.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1718354069.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1718354069-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1718354069-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1718354069-768x402.jpg%20768w%2