f%20the%20modern%20world%E2%80%94is%20the%20function%20of%20teaching%2C%20elevating%20and%20enlightening%20those%20who%20fall%20within%20the%20range%20of%20its%20influence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20who%20was%20this%20brave%20journalist%2C%20and%20why%20did%20he%20involve%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F235308%2Fsupreme-court-daughters-sons-equal-right-property-coparcener-mishra-mary-roy-arundhati-educationist-hindu-succession-act-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehimself%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20%3C%2Fa%3Eagainst%20the%20%E2%80%98Maharaj%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20here%20is%20a%20bite%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20public%20servant%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201832%20to%20a%20family%20of%20the%20Kapol%20Caste%2C%20a%20trading%20caste%20of%20Western%20India%2C%20Karsandas%20was%20always%20dedicated%20to%20public%20service.%20He%20was%20an%20active%20member%20of%20the%20Gujarati%20Gnanprasarak%20Mandalli%20(Gujarati%20Society%20for%20the%20Spread%20of%20Knowledge)%2C%20founded%20by%20the%20Students%E2%80%99%20Society%20of%20Elphinstone%20College.%20Among%20his%20classmates%20were%20prominent%20reformers%20such%20as%20poet%20Narmad%20and%20educationist%20Mahipatram%20Neelkanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20article%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%201851%2C%20he%20penned%20an%20essay%20for%20a%20literary%20competition%2C%20advocating%20for%20widow%20remarriage.%20When%20the%20news%20reached%20Karsandas%E2%80%99%20elderly%20aunt%2C%20who%20had%20cared%20for%20him%20following%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20she%20promptly%20evicted%20him%20from%20her%20home.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Karsandas%20was%20married.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20neither%20society%20nor%20familial%20pressure%20could%20stop%20Karsandas%20from%20following%20his%20journalistic%20instincts.%20Wanting%20to%20be%20more%20free%20with%20his%20writing%20and%20ideas%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20start%20his%20own%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20some%20friends%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F171267%2Fmadurai-gandhi-iconic-dress-loincloth-freedom-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20started%20a%20Gujarati%20weekly%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20around%201855%20called%20%3Cem%3ESatyaprakash%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20further%20his%20work%20of%20social%20interest.%20The%20weekly%20magazine%20was%20known%20for%20boldly%20confronting%20outdated%20Indian%20traditions%20and%20societal%20evils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FScreenshot-2024-06-12-184745-2-1718203040-500x561.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Netflix%20Film%20Maharaj%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FScreenshot-2024-06-12-184745-2-1718203040-500x561.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FScreenshot-2024-06-12-184745-2-1718203040-268x300.jpg%20268w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FScreenshot-2024-06-12-184745-2-1718203040-150x168.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FScreenshot-2024-06-12-184745-2-1718203040.jpg%20504w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352922%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22561%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENetflix%20Film%20Maharaj%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EIndianliberals.in%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20paper%20had%20a%20meagre%20subscription%20of%20500%2C%20yet%20its%20impact%20on%20Bombay%E2%80%99s%20conservative%20Gujarati%20Hindu%20community%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20overstated.%20In%20the%201850s%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20edit%20a%20series%20of%20newspapers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20Pushtimarg%20sect%20and%20Maharaj%E2%80%99s%20role%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarsandas%20was%20a%20follower%20of%20the%20Pushtimarg%20sect%2C%20founded%20by%20Vallabhacharya%20in%20the%2016th%20century%2C%20a%20prominent%20Hindu%20devotional%20sect%20in%20western%20India.%20By%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20Pushtimarg%20had%20amassed%20significant%20wealth%20and%20influence%2C%20with%20its%20spiritual%20leaders%2C%20known%20as%20Maharajs%2C%20wielding%20considerable%20power%20over%20their%20followers.%20These%20leaders%20were%20revered%20as%20living%20incarnations%20of%20Krishna%20and%20enjoyed%20a%20lavish%20lifestyle%20supported%20by%20the%20donations%20of%20devotees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Maharajas%20often%20faced%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20impropriety%20and%20corruption%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20growing%20rift%20between%20traditionalists%20and%20reform-minded%20individuals%20by%20the%20late%201800s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20himself%20also%20started%20to%20question%20the%20viability%20of%20the%20faith%20through%20his%20writings.%20In%201861%2C%20he%20published%20an%20article%20titled%20%3Cem%3EHinduono%20Asal%20Dharma%20ane%20Haalna%20Pakhandi%20Mato%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20Primitive%20Religion%20of%20the%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Present%20Heterodox%20Opinions)%2C%20which%20delivered%20the%20heaviest%20blow%20on%20the%20Maharaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20charges%2C%20it%20accused%20them%20of%20having%20sexual%20alliances%20with%20their%20female%20devotees.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20led%20to%20the%20Maharaj%20filing%20the%20famous%20libel%20case%20in%20the%20Bombay%20court%3B%20it%20was%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgreatest%20trial%20of%20modern%20times%20since%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fchapter%2F10.1057%2F9780230306004_2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrial%20of%20Warren%20Hastings%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20paper%20posted%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20University%20of%20Toronto%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20article%20in%20question%20not%20only%20denounced%20the%20Pushtimarg%20as%20heterodox%2C%20a%20latter-day%20corruption%20of%20the%20original%20Vedic%20religion%3B%20it%20also%20specifically%20accused%20Jadunathji%20of%20imposing%20himself%20sexually%20on%20his%20female%20devotees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadunathji%20Brijratanji%20Maharaj%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20worth%20Rs%2050%2C000%20against%20Karsandas%20for%20harming%20his%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20historic%20ruling%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharaj%20might%20have%20hoped%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F159978%2Fabortion-india-rules-how-to-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBombay%20Supreme%20Court%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewould%20clear%20his%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20name%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20he%20was%20sorely%20mistaken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20of%20the%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20held%20before%20a%20full%20court%2C%20presided%20over%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Mathew%20Sausse%20and%20Joseph%20Arnould.%20The%20case%20attracted%20significant%20interest%20from%20the%20press%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20members%20of%20the%20public%20attended%20the%20court%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352925%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarsandas%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20same%20community%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20and%20was%20threatened%20to%20be%20excommunicated.%20%E2%80%9CThirty-one%20witnesses%20for%20the%20plaintiff%20and%20thirty-three%20witnesses%20for%20the%20defendants%20were%20examined%3B%20Jadunath%20Maharaj%20was%20brought%20to%20court%2C%20which%20ultimately%20dismissed%20his%20defamation%20charges%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20the%20sect%E2%80%99s%20philosophies%20were%20examined%20and%20compared%20with%20other%20Hindu%20texts%20by%20missionary%20orientalist%20scholars%20and%20philosophers%20like%20John%20Wilson.%20Doctors%2C%20including%20Bhau%20Daji%20who%20was%20a%20known%20Indian%20physician%2C%20Sanskrit%20scholar%20and%20an%20antiquarian%2C%20testified%20that%20they%20had%20treated%20the%20religious%20leader%20for%20syphilis%2C%20and%20several%20witnesses%20recounted%20his%20erotic%20escapades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20featured%20dramatic%20testimonies%20from%20various%20witnesses%2C%20including%20women%20who%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20exploited%20by%20the%20Maharaj.%20These%20testimonies%20were%20crucial%20in%20substantiating%20Karsandas%E2%80%99%20allegations%20and%20painted%20a%20stark%20picture%20of%20the%20abuses%20of%20power%20within%20the%20sect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20came%20to%20a%20close%20on%2022%20April%2C%201862%2C%20with%20a%20judgment%20in%20favour%20of%20Karsandas%20Mulji.%20The%20court%20awarded%20him%20Rs%2011%2C500%2C%20as%20he%20had%20to%20bear%20a%20total%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%2014%2C000%20during%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClosing%20the%20case%20Judge%20Arnould%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20theology%20that%20has%20been%20before%20us!%20It%20is%20a%20question%20of%20morality.%20The%20principle%20for%20which%20the%20defendant%20and%20his%20witnesses%20have%20been%20contending%20is%20simply%20this%3A%20That%20what%20is%20morally%20wrong%20cannot%20be%20theologically%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarsandas%20passed%20away%20in%201871%20and%20is%20remembered%20fondly%20as%20the%20social%20reformer-journalist%20for%20his%20journalistic%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%20%26amp%3B%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00856401.2015.1050161%3Fscroll%3Dtop%26needAccess%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00856401.2015.1050161%3Fscroll%3Dtop%26needAccess%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eow%20to%20Defame%20a%20God%3A%20Public%20Selfhood%20in%20the%20Maharaj%20Libel%20Case%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20J%20Barton%20Scott%2C%20Published%20on%2018%20August%202015%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%2