ave%20gone%20from%20reusing%2045%25%20of%20their%20water%20on%20average%20to%20around%2080%25.%20This%20is%20why%20major%20players%20in%20the%20industry%20are%20adopting%20our%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20as%20Mansi%20notes%2C%20the%20ease%20of%20integrating%20Digital%20Paani%2C%20which%20functions%20on%20a%20plug-and-play%20model%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20enhances%20its%20appeal%E2%80%9D.%20Treatment%20facilities%20of%20any%20size%20and%20type%20can%20be%20installed%20in%20three%20straightforward%20steps%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Site%20survey%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20%5BParallel%5D%20Any%20IoT%20deployment%20needed%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20%5BParallel%5D%20Plant%20onboarding%20onto%20our%20software%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20whole%20process%20only%20takes%2030%20to%2045%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20industries%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20has%20also%20made%20forays%20into%20the%20residential%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20continuous%20expertise%20for%20regular%20operations%20as%20well%20as%20guidance%20on%20the%20needed%20retrofits%20so%20that%20they%20can%20get%20their%20STP%20completely%20streamlined%20and%20treat%20and%20reuse%20their%20water.%20We%20have%20converted%20many%20residential%20STPs%20from%20dysfunctional%20to%20reusing%2070%25%20of%20water%20in%20flushing%2C%20horticulture%2C%20and%20more.%20Many%20customers%20used%20to%20receive%20notices%20and%20fines%20from%20the%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20earlier%20because%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20manage%20their%20operations%2C%20and%20we%20have%20solved%20that%20for%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAdaptable%20to%20different%20environments%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20software%20is%20highly%20flexible%2C%20featuring%20comprehensive%20configuration%20panels%20that%20simplify%20the%20integration%20of%20plants%20of%20different%20sizes%20and%20technologies.%20On%20the%20backend%2C%20we%20have%20onboarded%20each%20key%20unit%20operation%20in%20water%20management%2C%20be%20it%20biological%20treatment%2C%20chemical%20treatment%2C%20RO%20systems%2C%20UF%20systems%20or%20more%2C%20so%20when%20we%20onboard%20a%20new%20unit%2C%20we%20simply%20tick%20that%20module%20and%20get%20the%20relevant%20analytics%2C%20automation%20flows%2C%20alerts%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20adapt%20to%20facilities%20of%20all%20kinds.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20team%20is%20well-equipped%20to%20provide%20expert%20support%20for%20any%20plant%20management%20as%20required.%20For%20instance%2C%20at%20present%2C%20we%20serve%20diverse%20needs%20including%20STP%20management%20for%20Taj%20Hotels%2C%20ETP%20management%20for%20Britannia%2C%20total%20water%20management%20for%20Plaksha%20University%2C%20and%20a%2070%20MLD%20STP%20in%20Dwarka%2C%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mansi%20Jain%20and%20her%20father%20Rajesh%20recently%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352685%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMansi%20Jain%20and%20her%20father%20Rajesh%20recently%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPan-India%20presence%20and%20funding%20their%20ambition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20is%20currently%20operational%20in%20about%2014%20states%20and%20has%20raised%20about%20%241.2%20million%20from%20global%20investors%20like%20Elemental%20Excelerator%20and%20Echo%20River%20Capital%20as%20well%20as%20Indian%20investors%20like%20Enzia%2C%20Peer%20Cheque%2C%20SAE%2C%20DevC%2C%20Bharat%20Founders%20Fund%2C%20and%20leading%20angels%20like%20Ashish%20Goel%20(Urban%20Ladder)%2C%20Yamini%20Bhatt%20(Wymo)%20and%20Mohit%20Tandon%20(Delhivery).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Karuna%20Jain%20and%20Shivam%20Jindal%20of%20Enzia%20Ventures%2C%20a%20venture%20capital%20fund%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enzia.vc%2Fperspective-posts%2Fwhy-we-invested-in-digital-paani%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esay%20about%20their%20decision%20to%20invest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20startup%2C%20%E2%80%9CDigital%20Paani%E2%80%99s%20solution%20seamlessly%20integrates%20into%20existing%20facilities%2C%20analysing%20the%20infrastructure%E2%80%99s%20needs%20based%20on%20multiple%20performance%20parameters%2C%20making%20these%20needs%20transparent%20to%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20and%20solving%20for%20these%20needs%20by%20automating%20unit%20operations%20and%20managing%20all%20human%20workflows%20including%20training%2C%20SOPs%2C%20and%20troubleshooting.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20helps%20ensure%20continuous%20and%20efficient%20operation%20of%20these%20plants%2C%20reducing%20energy%2C%20breakdown%2C%20manpower%2C%20and%20ch