3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20the%20problem%20statement%2C%20he%20spent%20the%20next%20two%20years%20understanding%20the%20agricultural%20market%2C%20credits%20and%20policies.%20With%20a%20mission%20to%20connect%20farmers%20with%20the%20large%20institutional%20buyers%2C%20he%20started%20Gram%20Unnati%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20idea%20is%20to%20help%20create%20a%20system%20where%20the%20producer%2C%20i.e.%20the%20farmer%2C%20knows%20what%20the%20customer%20wants%20and%20grows%20according%20to%20the%20specifications.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20understand%20what%20the%20demand%20is%2C%20where%20it%20is%20coming%20from%2C%20and%20then%20work%20with%20the%20farmers%20to%20help%20them%20produce%20accordingly.%20The%20next%20step%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20use%20the%20best%20seeds%2C%20build%20the%20supply%20chains%20around%20them%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20receive%20a%20fair%20price%20for%20their%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGram%20Unnati%20started%20working%20with%20soybean%20and%20mustard%20farmers%20in%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Jawasa%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20shares%20that%20the%20growth%20of%20his%20crops%20has%20increased%20and%20crop%20infections%20have%20reduced%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20income%20since%20his%20association%20with%20Gram%20Unnati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20them%20for%20two%20years.%20A%20Gram%20Unnati%20employee%20visits%20my%20field%20twice%20every%20week%20to%20check%20on%20the%20crops.%20They%20provide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312852%2Fpune-entrepreneur-launches-renewable-energy-marketplace-for-farmers-agrivijay-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebetter%20quality%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fertilisers%20and%20solutions%20for%20most%20of%20our%20probl