gest%20advantage%20is%20that%20you%20are%20not%20compromising%20on%20any%20of%20the%20uses%20while%20also%20contributing%20towards%20the%20betterment%20of%20our%20planet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20startup%20is%20commercialising%20its%20packaging%20solutions%20to%2050%20clients%20in%20the%20B2B%20sector%2C%20including%20restaurants%20and%20cafeterias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20work%2C%20Khushboo%20has%20been%20able%20to%20divert%20tonnes%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291567%2Fmumbai-family-sells-honeycomb-packaging-alternative-to-plastic-bubble-wrap-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20packaging%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewaste%2C%20but%20she%20believes%20a%20lot%20more%20work%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20in%20replacing%20multi-layer%20packaging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20now%20designing%20sheets%20using%20seaweed%20that%20are%20specifically%20supposed%20to%20replace%20the%20transparent%20plastic%20sheets%20directly%20which%20are%20used%20widely%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20success%20of%20her%20startup%2C%20Khushboo%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20a%20meaningful%20journey.%20It%20took%20time%20to%20make%20way%20through%20the%20packaging%20industry%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20male-dominated%20industry.%20As%20a%20female%20founder%2C%20you%20really%20have%20to%20be%20very%20headstrong%20in%20terms%20of%20leading%20the%20company.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20doubted%20our%20capabilities.%20But%20we%20either%20could%20have%20held%20ourselves%20back%20or%20been%20enthusiastic%20about%20our%20work.%20I%20choose%20the%20latter.%20The%20impact%20that%20we%20see%20makes%20me%20very%20positive%20about%20the%20work%20we%20do%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20change%20it%20can%20bring%20in%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%